msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:1056
msgid ""
"This section contains basic information in order to help troubleshoot issues "
"found when using FreeBSD as a Xen(TM) host or guest."
